motion_en: This House Believes that India should prioritise policies that aim to significantly reduce economic inequality rather than prioritise policies that aim to rapidly drive economic growth.
motion_zh: 本院认为，印度应优先推行旨在大幅减少经济不平等的政策，而非优先推行旨在快速推动经济增长的政策。
